OL,3,CHelicopter crash: 'scandalous' inquest
OL,4,Cwait for Leicester City owner's family
OL,6,FThe family of the lateowner killed in
OL,7,Fa helicopter crash says the six-year
OL,8,Fwait for an inquest, is "scandalous".
OL,10,FA pre-inquest review has taken place
OL,11,Fto set out the issues to be explored
OL,12,Finto the
OL,14,FFormer Foxes chairman Vichai
OL,15,FSrivaddhanaprabha, pilot Eric Swaffer,
OL,16,Fco-pilot Izabela Roza Lechowicz, and
OL,17,Ffellow passengers Kaveporn Punpare and
OL,18,FNusara Suknamai died when a helicopter
OL,19,Fspun out of control and burst into
OL,20,Fflames on October 27th 2018, in the
OL,21,Fcar park of the King Power Stadium.
