OL,6,FLawyers told today's hearing that
OL,7,Fmaking the victims' families wait
OL,8,Fyears for answers is a "national
OL,9,Fdisgrace".
OL,11,FThe crash happened just two years
OL,12,Fsince the club surprised the football
OL,13,Fworld by winning the Premier League.
OL,15,FIn September 2023, said mechanical
OL,16,Ffailures were to blame, and described
OL,17,Fthe crash as a "tragic accident".
